static char global_long_help_string[] = "[compress] Compresses ascii:\n\tbase64 (arg1) = Converts, compresses, and then prints data in base64.\n\tfile (arg1), (arg2) = Compresses the contents of an input file into an output file.\n\traw (arg1) = Prints a compressed string.\n\tstring (arg1) = Prints a string, compressed, and converted to base64.\n\n[decompress] Decompresses ascii:\n\tbase64 (arg1) = Converts, decompresses, and then prints a string in base64.\n\tfile (arg1), (arg2) = Decompresses the contents of an input file into an output file.\n\traw (arg1) = Prints a decompressed string.\n\tstring (arg1) = Prints a string, decompressed, and converted to base64.\n\n[help] Displays help information.\n\n[read (arg1)] Prints the decompressed contents of a compressed file.\n";